Meanwhile, there's
no one to see you

38:49.995 --> 38:52.429
In your altogether except me.

38:52.431 --> 38:54.597
How are you allowed
to wander around the castle?

38:54.599 --> 38:56.733
Well, I told them I was
preparing an appeal

38:56.735 --> 38:59.035
To be lodged with the
ecclesiastical court.

38:59.037 --> 39:02.439
Of course, we all know how
pointless that would be.

39:05.443 --> 39:07.477
Don't call out.

39:07.479 --> 39:08.845
This is madness.

39:08.847 --> 39:10.613
A few days ago,
I'd have thought so.

39:10.615 --> 39:12.415
Now I have no alternative.

39:12.417 --> 39:13.750
We both must die.

39:13.752 --> 39:15.385
You've already lost.

39:15.387 --> 39:17.454
You have nothing to gain
from killing me.

39:17.456 --> 39:19.456
I'm a mother.

39:19.458 --> 39:20.523
And a mother

39:20.525 --> 39:21.658
Who won't be here to be sure

39:21.660 --> 39:23.526
That her children are safe.

39:23.528 --> 39:25.495
But I can give them one thing.

39:25.497 --> 39:27.430
I can remove you before I go.

39:27.432 --> 39:30.500
I mean your children no harm.

39:30.502 --> 39:32.535
What do your good
intentions matter?

39:32.537 --> 39:35.705
I kill you, and the marriage
with sebastian is gone.

39:35.707 --> 39:39.142
My children's
inheritance restored.

39:39.144 --> 39:42.379
I kill you, and ensure
that you can never be

39:42.381 --> 39:44.714
The cause of francis's death.

39:44.716 --> 39:46.383
(coughs)

39:46.385 --> 39:49.986
It's the best legacy
that I can offer.

39:49.988 --> 39:52.622
(gasping for air)

39:54.525 --> 39:57.727
I hope you'll excuse
the choice of poison.

39:57.729 --> 40:00.430
I know death takes
a bit longer.

40:00.432 --> 40:02.866
But I didn't want
to be cruel.

40:02.868 --> 40:06.636
I promise that
you'll feel no pain.

40:09.039 --> 40:10.473
(door opens)

40:21.152 --> 40:22.685
(knocking)
man: Who goes there?

40:22.687 --> 40:25.822
Your grace?!

40:25.824 --> 40:28.992
(coughing)
(man shouting)

40:28.994 --> 40:31.528
Wake up, mother!
(knocking)

40:31.530 --> 40:33.062
Wake up, mother!

40:33.064 --> 40:34.464
Man:
Open the door now!

40:34.466 --> 40:36.166
Wake up, mother!

40:36.168 --> 40:38.568
Wake up, mother.

40:38.570 --> 40:41.004
No.

40:42.440 --> 40:44.541
They told me
you were dead.

40:44.543 --> 40:46.643
Man: Open the door!
You should be dead.

40:47.845 --> 40:50.613
(coughing)
and so should I.

40:50.615 --> 40:51.514
But I'm saving you.

40:52.850 --> 40:55.185
Get away from me! Go!

40:55.187 --> 40:56.186
Get out!

40:56.188 --> 40:57.787
(wheezing)

40:57.789 --> 40:59.856
(coughing)
(grunts)

40:59.858 --> 41:02.892
Don't touch them.
They might be poisoned.

41:02.894 --> 41:04.594
Mary.

41:04.596 --> 41:06.162
(panting)

41:07.565 --> 41:10.600
Mary. Are you all right?
What happened?

41:12.770 --> 41:14.103
(coughing)

41:16.106 --> 41:20.043
Catherine tried
to kill me.

41:20.045 --> 41:21.644
Take her away.

41:21.646 --> 41:23.079
Chain her up

41:23.081 --> 41:24.781
Like the animal she is!

41:25.883 --> 41:26.950
(coughing, panting)

41:30.921 --> 41:33.223
You should have left France
while you had the chance!

41:33.225 --> 41:34.791
He's a man with secrets.

41:34.793 --> 41:37.160
You've made a choice
that will be your ruin!

41:37.162 --> 41:39.095
I know who he is.

41:39.097 --> 41:40.997
And I've made
the perfect choice.

41:40.999 --> 41:43.566
Because together,
we have killed you.

